\par }\pard \qj\sa120 {\f4 \ldblquote Rabl\'f3m\'f3dra ront re\'e1m az \'e9hs\'e9g\rdblquote  - \'fagymond Zarathustra. - \ldblquote Erd\'f5ben \'e9s mocsarak k\'f6z\'f6tt ront re\'e1m \'e9hs\'e9gem, m\'e9lys\'e9ges \'e9jszak\'e1ban.
