\par }\pard \qj\sa120 {\f4 Imhol: a sorvad\'f3 lelk\'fcek; alig sz\'fclettek s m\'e1ris a f\'e1rads\'e1g \'e9s lemond\'e1s tanait s\'f3v\'e1rogj\'e1k.
